"Hecata %(hecata)s: %(cappadocian_crypt)s, %(powerbase_munich)s, %(split_the_veil)s, %(psychophagia)s, "
"%(paths_in_two_worlds)s, %(bone_shambler)s, %(rotting_behemoth)s"

#: codex_of_the_damned/templates/strategy/articles/basic/what-should-i-buy.html:1327
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Salubri %(salubri)s: %(angels_gift)s, %(anticipation)s, %(hunting_the_beast)s, %(righteous_blade)s, "
"%(tranquility_shield)s"
msgstr ""
"Salubri %(salubri)s: %(angels_gift)s, %(anticipation)s, %(hunting_the_beast)s, %(righteous_blade)s, "
"%(tranquility_shield)s"

#: codex_of_the_damned/templates/strategy/articles/basic/what-should-i-buy.html:1339
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Tzimisce %(tzimisce)s: %(fleshforge_chamber)s, %(szlachta_assistant)s, %(szlachta_bodyguard)s, %(vozhd_gravesend)s, "
"%(vozhd_juiz_de_fora)s, %(vozhd_szczecin)s"
msgstr ""
"Tzimisce %(tzimisce)s: %(fleshforge_chamber)s, %(szlachta_assistant)s, %(szlachta_bodyguard)s, %(vozhd_gravesend)s, "
"%(vozhd_juiz_de_fora)s, %(vozhd_szczecin)s"

#: codex_of_the_damned/templates/strategy/articles/basic/what-should-i-buy.html:1352
#, python-format
msgid "Ravnos %(ravnos)s: %(black_market_cache)s, %(contraband)s, %(dogged_pursuit)s, %(go_getter)s, %(phantasmagoria)s"
msgstr "Ravnos %(ravnos)s: %(black_market_cache)s, %(contraband)s, %(dogged_pursuit)s, %(go_getter)s, %(phantasmagoria)s"

#: codex_of_the_damned/templates/strategy/articles/basic/what-should-i-buy.html:1365
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Beyond the brand-new cards, these decks are a reprint goldmine. Hecata %(hecata)s brings back %(martyrs_resilience)s,"
" Lasombra %(lasombra)s reprints %(monster)s, and Ravnos %(ravnos)s is a trove of old flavor with %(ravnos_cache)s, "
"%(ak_47)s, %(kumpania)s and %(hide_the_mind)s. Tzimisce %(tzimisce)s digs up %(unlicensed_taxicab)s, %(crypts_sons)s "
"and %(far_mastery)s, while Salubri %(salubri)s reprints %(sight_beyond_sight)s."
msgstr ""
"Más allá de las cartas totalmente nuevas, estos mazos son una mina de reimpresiones. Hecata %(hecata)s recupera "
"%(martyrs_resilience)s, Lasombra %(lasombra)s reimprime %(monster)s, y Ravnos %(ravnos)s es un tesoro de sabor "
"clásico con %(ravnos_cache)s, %(ak_47)s, %(kumpania)s y %(hide_the_mind)s. Tzimisce %(tzimisce)s desentierra "
"%(unlicensed_taxicab)s, %(crypts_sons)s y %(far_mastery)s, mientras que Salubri %(salubri)s reimprime "
"%(sight_beyond_sight)s."

#: codex_of_the_damned/templates/strategy/articles/basic/what-should-i-buy.html:1387
msgid "Kickstarter"
msgstr "Kickstarter"

#: codex_of_the_damned/templates/strategy/articles/basic/what-should-i-buy.html:1390
#, python-format
msgid ""
"If you were wandering around during the blip (the 2010-2017 period with no physical print), you may know of the VEKN "
"\"PDF expansion\". You might want to know they've been printed through a %(kickstarter)s, and a few copies are still "
"available in online shops around, specifically on the %(bcp_online_shop)s. You might want to get your claws on those "
"cards to replace your paper prints there. Also %(show_of_force)s, %(public_vilification)s and %(inside_dirt)s, from "
"Danse Macabre, have been boosted."
msgstr ""
"Si andabas rondando durante el blip (el período 2010-2017 sin impresión física), quizás conozcas la «expansión en "
"PDF» de la VEKN. Te interesará saber que se imprimieron gracias a un %(kickstarter)s, y todavía quedan algunas copias"
" disponibles en tiendas en línea, en particular en la %(bcp_online_shop)s. Puede que quieras poner tus garras sobre "
"esas cartas para reemplazar tus impresiones caseras. Además, %(show_of_force)s, %(public_vilification)s e "
"%(inside_dirt)s, de Danse Macabre, han sido potenciadas."

#: codex_of_the_damned/templates/strategy/articles/basic/what-should-i-buy.html:1394
msgid "BCP online shop"
msgstr "tienda en línea de BCP"

#: codex_of_the_damned/templates/strategy/articles/basic/what-should-i-buy.html:1411
msgid "Promo Packs 2 & 3"
msgstr "Promo Packs 2 & 3"

#: codex_of_the_damned/templates/strategy/articles/basic/what-should-i-buy.html:1416
msgid "Promo Pack 2"
msgstr "Promo Pack 2"

#: codex_of_the_damned/templates/strategy/articles/basic/what-should-i-buy.html:1414
#, python-format
msgid ""
"%(promo_pack_2)s contains a few Barons you will not find elsewhere: %(benedito_a_lanterna)s, %(bituin)s, and "
"%(jacques_rouge)s."
msgstr ""
"%(promo_pack_2)s contiene algunos Barones que no encontrarás en ningún otro lugar: %(benedito_a_lanterna)s, "
"%(bituin)s y %(jacques_rouge)s."

#: codex_of_the_damned/templates/strategy/articles/basic/what-should-i-buy.html:1428
msgid "Promo Pack 3"
msgstr "Promo Pack 3"

#: codex_of_the_damned/templates/strategy/articles/basic/what-should-i-buy.html:1426
#, python-format
msgid ""
"%(promo_pack_3)s is likewise built around exclusive vampires, one per core clan: %(gilbert_duane)s %(malkavian)s, "
"%(victoria_ash)s %(toreador)s, %(okulos)s %(nosferatu)s, %(karl_schrekt)s %(tremere)s and %(fiorenza_savona)s "
"%(ventrue)s. It also bundles handy reprints like %(judgment)s."
msgstr ""
"%(promo_pack_3)s está construido, del mismo modo, en torno a vampiros exclusivos, uno por cada clan principal: "
"%(gilbert_duane)s %(malkavian)s, %(victoria_ash)s %(toreador)s, %(okulos)s %(nosferatu)s, %(karl_schrekt)s "
"%(tremere)s y %(fiorenza_savona)s %(ventrue)s. También incluye reimpresiones prácticas como %(judgment)s."

#: codex_of_the_damned/templates/strategy/articles/basic/what-should-i-buy.html:1445
msgid "V5"
msgstr "V5"

#: codex_of_the_damned/templates/strategy/articles/basic/what-should-i-buy.html:1448
#, python-format
msgid ""
"The five V5 base decks have brought new vampires in groups 6 and 7, though they didn't quite disrupt the meta the way"
" the other V5 expansions did. All V5 base bundles contain new vampires so, if you're a completionist, you will want a"
" bit of everything there. Moreover, the decks include a good number of staples that might be neat in your collection:"
" you never have enough %(second_tradition)s, %(parity_shift)s, %(govern_the_unaligned)s, %(eyes_of_argus)s, "
"%(deflection)s and %(delaying_tactics)s, right?"
msgstr ""
"Los cinco mazos base V5 han traído vampiros nuevos en los grupos 6 y 7, aunque no llegaron a alterar el metajuego "
"como sí hicieron las demás expansiones V5. Todos los paquetes base V5 contienen vampiros nuevos, así que, si eres un "
"completista, querrás tener un poco de todo. Además, los mazos incluyen un buen número de cartas imprescindibles que "
"podrían quedar bien en tu colección: nunca tienes suficientes %(second_tradition)s, %(parity_shift)s, "
"%(govern_the_unaligned)s, %(eyes_of_argus)s, %(deflection)s y %(delaying_tactics)s, ¿verdad?"

#: codex_of_the_damned/templates/strategy/articles/basic/what-should-i-buy.html:1465
#, python-format
msgid ""
"In terms of library cards, <strong>V5 Nosferatu</strong> %(nosferatu)s is the only deck introducing new cards: "
"%(creeping_sabotage)s, %(protected_district)s, %(the_warrens)s and %(roundhouse)s."
msgstr ""
"En cuanto a cartas de biblioteca, <strong>V5 Nosferatu</strong> %(nosferatu)s es el único mazo que introduce cartas "
"nuevas: %(creeping_sabotage)s, %(protected_district)s, %(the_warrens)s y %(roundhouse)s."

#: codex_of_the_damned/templates/strategy/articles/basic/what-should-i-buy.html:1481
#, python-format
msgid "%(fall_of_london)s contains a couple of additional vampires, and a couple of new Library cards:"
msgstr "%(fall_of_london)s contiene un par de vampiros adicionales, y un par de nuevas cartas de Biblioteca:"

#: codex_of_the_damned/templates/strategy/articles/basic/what-should-i-buy.html:1489
#, python-format
msgid ""
"<li>%(the_british_museum_london)s</li> <li>%(the_mithraeum_london)s</li> <li>%(mithraic_cultist)s</li> "
"<li>%(mobile_hq_operation_antigen)s</li> <li>%(the_shard_london)s</li> <li>%(ectu_operative)s</li> "
"<li>%(michael_harris_the_incinerator)s</li> <li>%(valerie_diaz_antigen_commander)s</li> "
"<li>%(enhanced_coagulant)s</li> <li>%(ritual_goblet)s</li>"
msgstr ""
"<li>%(the_british_museum_london)s</li> <li>%(the_mithraeum_london)s</li> <li>%(mithraic_cultist)s</li> "
"<li>%(mobile_hq_operation_antigen)s</li> <li>%(the_shard_london)s</li> <li>%(ectu_operative)s</li> "
"<li>%(michael_harris_the_incinerator)s</li> <li>%(valerie_diaz_antigen_commander)s</li> "
"<li>%(enhanced_coagulant)s</li> <li>%(ritual_goblet)s</li>"

#: codex_of_the_damned/templates/strategy/articles/basic/what-should-i-buy.html:1514
#, python-format
msgid "The %(british_museum)s in particular has been used successfully in a couple of builds."
msgstr "El %(british_museum)s en particular se ha usado con éxito en algunas construcciones de mazo."

#: codex_of_the_damned/templates/strategy/articles/basic/what-should-i-buy.html:1526
#, python-format
msgid ""
"If you've missed it, you'll want to look into the %(lost_kindred)s bundle and the infamous %(emerald_legionnaire)s. "
"The card was designed to boost the Harbingers %(harbinger_of_skulls)s a bit and give them a chance in competitive "
"play, and ended up giving them a couple of top tier tournament decks so strong the meta had to adapt and include more"
" solutions against the typical swarm of allies these decks can field. So much so that the card was errated in "
"February 2024, making Emerald decks less of a thing, and acquiring this bundle less appealing."
msgstr ""
"Si te lo perdiste, querrás echar un vistazo al paquete %(lost_kindred)s y al infame %(emerald_legionnaire)s. La carta"
" fue diseñada para potenciar un poco a los Harbingers %(harbinger_of_skulls)s y darles una oportunidad en el juego "
"competitivo, y terminó dándoles un par de mazos de torneo de máximo nivel tan fuertes que el metajuego tuvo que "
"adaptarse e incluir más soluciones contra el habitual enjambre de aliados que estos mazos pueden desplegar. Tanto es "
"así que la carta recibió un erratum en febrero de 2024, lo que hizo que los mazos Emerald fueran mucho menos "
"relevantes, y que adquirir este paquete resultara menos atractivo."

#: codex_of_the_damned/templates/strategy/articles/basic/what-should-i-buy.html:1539
#, python-format
msgid ""
"On top of it, the expansion offers nice new toys for Gargoyles %(gargoyle)s, Samedi %(samedi)s, Salubri antitribu "
"%(salubri_antitribu)s and Blood Brothers %(blood_brother)s."
msgstr ""
"Además, la expansión ofrece nuevos y agradables juguetes para los Gargoyles %(gargoyle)s, Samedi %(samedi)s, Salubri "
"antitribu %(salubri_antitribu)s y Blood Brothers %(blood_brother)s."

#: codex_of_the_damned/templates/strategy/articles/basic/what-should-i-buy.html:1547
msgid "What changed in the last few years?"
msgstr "¿Qué ha cambiado en los últimos años?"

#: codex_of_the_damned/templates/strategy/articles/basic/what-should-i-buy.html:1551
msgid "detailed list of changes"
msgstr "lista detallada de cambios"

#: codex_of_the_damned/templates/strategy/articles/basic/what-should-i-buy.html:1549
#, python-format
msgid ""
"There have been a number of changes recently. You can browse the %(detailed_list_of_changes)s but, to give you a "
"primer on the most important points:"
msgstr ""
"Ha habido varios cambios recientemente. Puedes consultar la %(detailed_list_of_changes)s pero, para darte un resumen "
"de los puntos más importantes:"

#: codex_of_the_damned/templates/strategy/articles/basic/what-should-i-buy.html:1558
msgid ""
"The Sabbat is back in V5: its vampires now follow one of four Paths (a Path of Enlightenment printed on the crypt "
"card), and two new keywords, Stun and Queue a combat, were introduced along with them."
msgstr ""
"El Sabbat está de vuelta en V5: sus vampiros ahora siguen uno de los cuatro Paths (un Path of Enlightenment impreso "
"en la carta de cripta), y se introdujeron junto con ellos dos palabras clave nuevas, Stun y Queue a combat."

#: codex_of_the_damned/templates/strategy/articles/basic/what-should-i-buy.html:1563
#, python-format
msgid "%(derange)s now explicitly changes the clan and sect of its target."
msgstr "%(derange)s ahora cambia explícitamente el clan y la secta de su objetivo."

#: codex_of_the_damned/templates/strategy/articles/basic/what-should-i-buy.html:1570
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Since 2011, %(psyche)s is played during combat, not in-between combats anymore, and priscii have \"ballots\", not "
"\"votes\"."
msgstr ""
"Desde 2011, %(psyche)s se juega durante el combate, ya no entre combates, y los priscii tienen \"papeletas\", no "
"\"votos\"."

#: codex_of_the_damned/templates/strategy/articles/basic/what-should-i-buy.html:1577
msgid ""
"Caitiff is a full-fledged clan, Anarch is a full-fledged sect, and sect is inherited from the sire when creating a "
"new vampire."
msgstr ""
"Caitiff es un clan de pleno derecho, Anarch es una secta de pleno derecho, y la secta se hereda del sire al crear un "
"vampiro nuevo."

#: codex_of_the_damned/templates/strategy/articles/basic/what-should-i-buy.html:1581
msgid "Vampires do not automatically get out during influence anymore: you choose whether you turn them up or not."
msgstr "Los vampiros ya no salen automáticamente durante la fase de influencia: tú decides si los sacas o no."

#: codex_of_the_damned/templates/strategy/articles/basic/what-should-i-buy.html:1585
msgid ""
"A lot of effects that were mandatory are now optional, and things that were fetched in secret now revealed, for a "
"smoother tournament experience"
msgstr ""
"Muchos efectos que antes eran obligatorios ahora son opcionales, y las cosas que se buscaban en secreto ahora se "
"revelan, para una experiencia de torneo más fluida"

#: codex_of_the_damned/templates/strategy/articles/basic/what-should-i-buy.html:1590
#, python-format
msgid "%(lilith_s_blessing)s was banned in 2013"
msgstr "%(lilith_s_blessing)s fue prohibida en 2013"

#: codex_of_the_damned/templates/strategy/articles/basic/what-should-i-buy.html:1596
#, python-format
msgid ""
"%(anthelios)s, %(temptation_of_greater_power)s and %(seeds_of_corruption)s were banned in 2016, and tap/untap have "
"been replaced by lock/unlock because of patent issues."
msgstr ""
"%(anthelios)s, %(temptation_of_greater_power)s y %(seeds_of_corruption)s fueron prohibidas en 2016, y tap/untap "
"fueron sustituidos por girar/enderezar por cuestiones de patente."

#: codex_of_the_damned/templates/strategy/articles/basic/what-should-i-buy.html:1605
#, python-format
msgid ""
"%(gypsies)s, %(rom_gypsy)s, %(tarbaby_jack)s, %(terrorists)s and %(tsigane)s were banned in 2020 but replaced by "
"%(double_deuce)s, %(city_star_taxi)s, %(len_konopka)s, %(dark_web_procurer)s and %(ashlesha)s."
msgstr ""
"%(gypsies)s, %(rom_gypsy)s, %(tarbaby_jack)s, %(terrorists)s y %(tsigane)s fueron prohibidas en 2020 pero sustituidas"
" por %(double_deuce)s, %(city_star_taxi)s, %(len_konopka)s, %(dark_web_procurer)s y %(ashlesha)s."

#: codex_of_the_damned/templates/strategy/articles/basic/what-should-i-buy.html:1622
#, python-format
msgid ""
"%(villein)s, %(pentex_subversion)s, %(una)s, %(ankara_citadel)s, %(parity_shift)s, %(sensory_deprivation)s, "
"%(nightmare_curse)s, %(ashur_tablets)s, and %(emerald_legionnaire)s have been nerfed."
msgstr ""
"%(villein)s, %(pentex_subversion)s, %(una)s, %(ankara_citadel)s, %(parity_shift)s, %(sensory_deprivation)s, "
"%(nightmare_curse)s, %(ashur_tablets)s y %(emerald_legionnaire)s han sido nerfeadas."

#: codex_of_the_damned/templates/strategy/articles/basic/what-should-i-buy.html:1638
#, python-format
msgid ""
"%(black_metamorphosis)s, %(summon_the_abyss)s, %(summon_the_serpent)s, %(shadow_parasite)s, "
"%(revelation_of_despair)s, %(the_realm_of_the_black_sun)s, %(principia_discordia)s, %(masquer)s, %(kali_s_fang)s, "
"%(giuseppe)s, %(edge_vitiation)s, %(divine_image)s, %(consignment_to_duat)s, %(inside_dirt)s, "
"%(public_vilification)s, %(show_of_force)s, %(vivienne_geroux)s, %(quickness)s, %(herald_of_topheth)s, "
"%(oxford_university_england)s, %(private_audience)s and %(cardinal_benediction)s have been boosted."
msgstr ""
"%(black_metamorphosis)s, %(summon_the_abyss)s, %(summon_the_serpent)s, %(shadow_parasite)s, "
"%(revelation_of_despair)s, %(the_realm_of_the_black_sun)s, %(principia_discordia)s, %(masquer)s, %(kali_s_fang)s, "
"%(giuseppe)s, %(edge_vitiation)s, %(divine_image)s, %(consignment_to_duat)s, %(inside_dirt)s, "
"%(public_vilification)s, %(show_of_force)s, %(vivienne_geroux)s, %(quickness)s, %(herald_of_topheth)s, "
"%(oxford_university_england)s, %(private_audience)s y %(cardinal_benediction)s han sido potenciadas."

#: codex_of_the_damned/templates/strategy/articles/basic/what-should-i-buy.html:1672
msgid "Worthy reprints"
msgstr "Reimpresiones destacadas"

#: codex_of_the_damned/templates/strategy/articles/basic/what-should-i-buy.html:1678
#, python-format
msgid ""
"In case you're not aware, you might want to know that a lot of legacy cards are available as print-on-demand on "
"%(drivethru_cards)s and %(gamepod)s for less then $0.50 apiece. You can finally complete your collections for clans:"
msgstr ""
"Por si no lo sabías, quizás te interese saber que muchas cartas legacy están disponibles en impresión bajo demanda en"
" %(drivethru_cards)s y %(gamepod)s por menos de $0,50 la unidad. Por fin puedes completar tus colecciones para los "
"clanes:"

#: codex_of_the_damned/templates/strategy/articles/basic/what-should-i-buy.html:1704
msgid "and disciplines:"
msgstr "y disciplinas:"

#: codex_of_the_damned/templates/strategy/articles/basic/what-should-i-buy.html:1720
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Never had the means to build a %(baltimore_purge)s, %(shambling_hordes)s, %(war_ghouls)s, %(ravnos_clown_car)s, "
"%(the_unnamed)s, %(giotto)s, %(spirit_marionette)s, %(shattering_crescendo)s, or %(legacy_of_pander)s deck? It's now "
"really affordable (mind the taxes and delivery fees, depending on where you live. It's still a good deal, though)."
msgstr ""
"¿Nunca tuviste los medios para construir un mazo %(baltimore_purge)s, %(shambling_hordes)s, %(war_ghouls)s, "
"%(ravnos_clown_car)s, %(the_unnamed)s, %(giotto)s, %(spirit_marionette)s, %(shattering_crescendo)s o "
"%(legacy_of_pander)s? Ahora es realmente asequible (ten en cuenta los impuestos y los gastos de envío, según dónde "
"vivas. Aun así, sigue siendo un buen trato)."

#: codex_of_the_damned/templates/strategy/articles/basic/what-should-i-buy.html:1743
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Maybe before you entered torpor, a few cards were frustratingly expensive to get. %(ashur_tablets)s, %(liquidation)s,"
" %(enkil_cog)s, %(carlton)s, %(heart_of_nizchetus)s and %(the_unmasking)s, for example. In that case, you'll happily "
"acquire a few copies of %(anthology_1)s. It was the first reprint since Heirs to the Blood in 2010, and this bundle "
"released at the 2017 Berlin European Championship launched BCP and the golden years we're unliving now."
msgstr ""
"Puede que antes de entrar en letargo, algunas cartas fueran frustrantemente caras de conseguir. %(ashur_tablets)s, "
"%(liquidation)s, %(enkil_cog)s, %(carlton)s, %(heart_of_nizchetus)s y %(the_unmasking)s, por ejemplo. En ese caso, te"
" alegrará hacerte con algunas copias de %(anthology_1)s. Fue la primera reimpresión desde Heirs to the Blood en 2010,"
" y este paquete, publicado en el Campeonato Europeo de Berlín de 2017, lanzó BCP y los años dorados que seguimos "
"desviviendo hasta hoy."

#: codex_of_the_damned/templates/strategy/articles/basic/what-should-i-buy.html:1767
#, python-format
msgid ""
"The %(anniversary)s preconstructed deck might also be a neat acquisition. It is a full-fledged top tier tournament "
"Stanislava deck, with all the good cards, including %(enkil_cog)s, %(dreams_of_the_sphinx)s, %(giant_s_blood)s, some "
"%(zillah_s_valley)s and %(villein)s, the first real print of %(ennoia_s_theater)s, some %(banishment)s and a fair "
"number of %(parity_shift)s. It's a real treat."
msgstr ""
"El mazo preconstruido %(anniversary)s también podría ser una buena adquisición. Es un mazo Stanislava de torneo de "
"máximo nivel de pleno derecho, con todas las buenas cartas, incluyendo %(enkil_cog)s, %(dreams_of_the_sphinx)s, "
"%(giant_s_blood)s, algunos %(zillah_s_valley)s y %(villein)s, la primera impresión real de %(ennoia_s_theater)s, "
"algunos %(banishment)s y un buen número de %(parity_shift)s. Es un auténtico regalo."

#: codex_of_the_damned/templates/strategy/articles/basic/what-should-i-buy.html:1789
msgid "Sabbat Precons"
msgstr "Precons Sabbat"

#: codex_of_the_damned/templates/strategy/articles/basic/what-should-i-buy.html:1792
#, python-format
msgid ""
"The other %(legacy_preconstructed_decks)s were released as high level preconstructed decks to allow neonates to join "
"existing Elder tables with something decent enough to leave them a chance. To make it worth our while, BCP also "
"seized this occasion to print rather heavily sought-after cards, like a bunch of %(antonio)s and %(nephandus)s in "
"%(pact_with_nephandi)s, so many %(embraces)s alongside a couple of %(palla_grande)s and %(foundation_exhibit)s in "
"%(libertine_ball)s, the whole Lasombra %(lasombra)s package together with %(jake_washington)s and "
"%(monastery_of_shadows)s in %(parliament_of_shadows)s, and the whole %(aus)s package with %(the_rack)s, "
"%(smiling_jack)s, %(bowl_of_convergence)s and %(heart_of_nizchetus)s in %(den_of_fiends)s."
msgstr ""
"Los otros %(legacy_preconstructed_decks)s se publicaron como mazos preconstruidos de alto nivel para permitir a los "
"neófitos unirse a mesas de Ancianos existentes con algo lo bastante decente como para tener una oportunidad. Para que"
" mereciera la pena, BCP también aprovechó la ocasión para imprimir cartas bastante codiciadas, como un buen puñado de"
" %(antonio)s y %(nephandus)s en %(pact_with_nephandi)s, tantos %(embraces)s junto con un par de %(palla_grande)s y "
"%(foundation_exhibit)s en %(libertine_ball)s, todo el paquete Lasombra %(lasombra)s junto con %(jake_washington)s y "
"%(monastery_of_shadows)s en %(parliament_of_shadows)s, y todo el paquete de %(aus)s con %(the_rack)s, "
"%(smiling_jack)s, %(bowl_of_convergence)s y %(heart_of_nizchetus)s en %(den_of_fiends)s."

#: codex_of_the_damned/templates/strategy/articles/basic/what-should-i-buy.html:1827
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Depending on where you're collection is at, these decks could really fill some holes there, and they also include all"
" the right staples you've never have enough of, like %(govern)s, %(deflection)s, %(eyes_of_argus)s, %(deep_song)s, "
"%(carrion_crows)s, etc."
msgstr ""
"Dependiendo de en qué punto esté tu colección, estos mazos podrían llenar bastantes huecos, y además incluyen todas "
"las cartas imprescindibles de las que nunca tienes suficientes, como %(govern)s, %(deflection)s, %(eyes_of_argus)s, "
"%(deep_song)s, %(carrion_crows)s, etc."

#: codex_of_the_damned/templates/strategy/articles/basic/what-should-i-buy.html:1842
msgid "Promo Pack 1"
msgstr "Promo Pack 1"

#: codex_of_the_damned/templates/strategy/articles/basic/what-should-i-buy.html:1845
#, python-format
msgid ""
"A nice treat, the %(promo_pack_1)s has all these juicy star vampires that were previously released as promo cards: "
"finally a chance to get this %(capuchin)s, %(montano)s or %(lord_tremere)s deck rolling for a really affordable "
"price."
msgstr ""
"Todo un regalo, el %(promo_pack_1)s tiene todos esos jugosos vampiros estrella que antes solo se publicaron como "
"cartas promocionales: por fin una oportunidad de poner en marcha ese mazo de %(capuchin)s, %(montano)s o "
"%(lord_tremere)s por un precio realmente asequible."

#: codex_of_the_damned/templates/strategy/articles/basic/what-should-i-buy.html:1860
msgid "Keepers of Traditions and Heirs to The Blood"
msgstr "Keepers of Traditions and Heirs to The Blood"

#: codex_of_the_damned/templates/strategy/articles/basic/what-should-i-buy.html:1863
#, python-format
msgid ""
"The %(keepers_of_tradition)s have some nice cards and vampires you might be lacking, it's worth looking into. The "
"%(heirs_to_the_blood)s where a very nice reprint, also with a bunch of hard to find bloodline cards, but now that "
"Baali %(baali)s, Daughters %(daughter_of_cacophony)s and Salubri %(salubri)s are available on print-on-demand, your "
"mileage might vary."
msgstr ""
"Los %(keepers_of_tradition)s tienen algunas cartas y vampiros interesantes que podrían faltarte, vale la pena "
"echarles un vistazo. Los %(heirs_to_the_blood)s fueron una reimpresión muy buena, también con un montón de cartas de "
"linaje difíciles de encontrar, pero ahora que los Baali %(baali)s, Daughters %(daughter_of_cacophony)s y Salubri "
"%(salubri)s están disponibles en impresión bajo demanda, los resultados pueden variar."

#: codex_of_the_damned/templates/strategy/articles/basic/what-should-i-buy.html:1878
msgid "For the collectors"
msgstr "Para los coleccionistas"

#: codex_of_the_damned/templates/strategy/articles/basic/what-should-i-buy.html:1881
msgid "exclusive promos"
msgstr "promos exclusivas"

#: codex_of_the_damned/templates/strategy/articles/basic/what-should-i-buy.html:1880
#, python-format
msgid ""
"A few of us Elders are greedy hoarders. That's fine, that's the beast speaking, really. You have to let it go from "
"time to time, right? Some pretty %(exclusive_promos)s have been released in the last few years, and there have been "
"successive prints and differences in bundles you might want to know about:"
msgstr ""
"Algunos de nosotros, los Ancianos, somos coleccionistas codiciosos. No pasa nada, es la Bestia hablando, en realidad."
" Hay que dejarla salir de vez en cuando, ¿no? Se han publicado algunas bonitas %(exclusive_promos)s en los últimos "
"años, y ha habido tiradas sucesivas y diferencias entre paquetes que quizás te interese conocer:"

#: codex_of_the_damned/templates/strategy/articles/basic/what-should-i-buy.html:1890
msgid ""
"<li> Some promos have been released with alternate are: more and more cards are getting a <strong>Full-bleed</strong>"
" version, there are two <strong>sketch versions</strong> of Direct Intervention, and <strong>alternate arts</strong> "
"for a few other cards. </li> <li> An <strong>Edge card</strong> that has been released as promo and is now also "
"available as print-on-demand. </li> <li> The <strong>Anthology set</strong> released and sold in Berlin in 2017 is "
"different from the Anthology 1 reprint: it had a few more cards (Andre, Aisha, The Line) and a different icon. </li> "
"<li> The pledgers of the <strong>Unleashed Kickstarter</strong>, the printed release of the VEKN \"PDF expansions\" "
"Anarch Unbound, Danse Macabre and The Unaligned, also got the promos Double Deuce, Ashlesha, Len Kanopka, Vivienne "
"Geroux, City Star Taxi, Dark Web Procurer and Vlad Tepes. </li> <li> Promos have <strong>no icon</strong>, the "
"reprints do. So there are multiple versions of the cards in the promo packs or on print-on-demand (All cards in promo"
" packs 1 and 2 were first released as promos with no icon, as was Nefertiti advanced or Anarch Convert, for example)."
" The cards that have been promos multiple time, like Entrancement and Charisma had no icon the first time, and a "
"<strong>specific GP icon</strong> (different for each) for the second promo round. </li> <li> They were exclusive "
"promos for some <strong>World of Darkness product</strong>: Bolesław Gutowski (Polish edition of VTM), Alicia Cortez "
"(Mind's Eye Theatre), Gabriel Tremblay (Chapters) and Tegyrius (War of Ages). They've all been reprinted as GP promos"
" </li> <li> V5 bundles have been release not only in English, but also in <strong>French</strong>, "
"<strong>Spanish</strong> and <strong>Portuguese</strong>. Some bundles were also release in <strong>Latin</strong>. "
"These might make for nice alternates in your decks, or constitute an additional challenge if you're a real "
"completionist. </li>"
msgstr ""
"<li> Algunas promos se han publicado con ilustraciones alternativas: cada vez más cartas tienen una versión <strong"
">Full-bleed</strong>, hay dos <strong>versiones a boceto</strong> de Direct Intervention, y <strong>ilustraciones "
"alternativas</strong> para algunas otras cartas. </li> <li> Se ha publicado una <strong>carta Edge</strong> como "
"promo, ahora también disponible en impresión bajo demanda. </li> <li> El <strong>set Anthology</strong> publicado y "
"vendido en Berlín en 2017 es diferente de la reimpresión Anthology 1: tenía algunas cartas más (Andre, Aisha, The "
"Line) y un icono distinto. </li> <li> Los mecenas del <strong>Unleashed Kickstarter</strong>, la edición impresa de "
"las \"expansiones en PDF\" de la VEKN Anarch Unbound, Danse Macabre y The Unaligned, también recibieron las promos "
"Double Deuce, Ashlesha, Len Kanopka, Vivienne Geroux, City Star Taxi, Dark Web Procurer y Vlad Tepes. </li> <li> Las "
"promos <strong>no tienen icono</strong>, las reimpresiones sí. Por eso hay varias versiones de las cartas en los "
"packs promocionales o en impresión bajo demanda (todas las cartas de los promo packs 1 y 2 se publicaron primero como"
" promos sin icono, como fue el caso de Nefertiti advanced o Anarch Convert, por ejemplo). Las cartas que han sido "
"promo varias veces, como Entrancement y Charisma, no tenían icono la primera vez, y tuvieron un <strong>icono GP "
"específico</strong> (distinto para cada una) en la segunda tanda de promoción. </li> <li> Fueron promos exclusivas "
"para algunos <strong>productos de World of Darkness</strong>: Bolesław Gutowski (edición polaca de VTM), Alicia "
"Cortez (Mind's Eye Theatre), Gabriel Tremblay (Chapters) y Tegyrius (War of Ages). Todas se han reimpreso como promos"
" GP </li> <li> Los paquetes V5 se han publicado no solo en inglés, sino también en <strong>francés</strong>, "
"<strong>español</strong> y <strong>portugués</strong>. Algunos paquetes también se publicaron en "
"<strong>latín</strong>. Podrían ser buenas alternativas para tus mazos, o suponer un reto adicional si eres un "
"auténtico completista. </li>"

